# Cross Validation Techniques in Machine Learning

This folder contains real-life case studies demonstrating different cross-validation techniques.

## Techniques Covered
1. Stratified K-Fold – Cancer Detection
2. Time Series Split – Stock Price Prediction
3. K-Fold – Customer Churn Prediction
4. Leave-One-Out – Rare Disease Research
5. Repeated K-Fold – Image Classification

## Tools Used
Python
Scikit-learn
NumPy
